org.apache.flink.runtime.checkpoint

类 CompletedCheckpointStats

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.checkpoint.AbstractCheckpointStats
      • org.apache.flink.runtime.checkpoint.CompletedCheckpointStats
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class CompletedCheckpointStats
extends AbstractCheckpointStats
    Statistics for a successfully completed checkpoint.

    The reported statistics are immutable except for the discarded flag, which is updated via the CompletedCheckpointStats.DiscardCallback and the CompletedCheckpoint after an instance of this class has been created.

      (专用程序包) class  CompletedCheckpointStats.DiscardCallback
      Callback for the CompletedCheckpoint instance to notify about disposal of the checkpoint (most commonly when the checkpoint has been subsumed by a newer one).

      • CompletedCheckpointStats

        CompletedCheckpointStats(long checkpointId,
                         long triggerTimestamp,
                         CheckpointProperties props,
                         int totalSubtaskCount,
                         java.util.Map<JobVertexID,TaskStateStats> taskStats,
                         int numAcknowledgedSubtasks,
                         long stateSize,
                         long alignmentBuffered,
                         SubtaskStateStats latestAcknowledgedSubtask,
                         @Nullable
                         java.lang.String externalPath)
        Creates a tracker for a CompletedCheckpoint.
        参数:
        checkpointId - ID of the checkpoint.
        triggerTimestamp - Timestamp when the checkpoint was triggered.
        props - Checkpoint properties of the checkpoint.
        totalSubtaskCount - Total number of subtasks for the checkpoint.
        taskStats - Task stats for each involved operator.
        numAcknowledgedSubtasks - Number of acknowledged subtasks.
        stateSize - Total checkpoint state size over all subtasks.
        alignmentBuffered - Buffered bytes during alignment over all subtasks.
        latestAcknowledgedSubtask - The latest acknowledged subtask stats.
        externalPath - Optional external path if persisted externally.
